165
00:12:00,800 --> 00:12:02,700
<font color=#DEDE00>Bangun, Nak.</font>

166
00:12:50,900 --> 00:12:52,100
<font color=#DEDE00><i>Kau sudah istirahat?</i></font>

167
00:12:52,100 --> 00:12:54,600
<font color=#DEDE00><i>Tugas memantau Pak Hwang sudah selesai.</i></font>

168
00:12:54,600 --> 00:12:56,900
<font color=#DEDE00><i>Jadi, akan kuberitahu subyek berikutnya
