171
00:13:02,200 --> 00:13:03,600
<font color=#DEDE00>Shi Yoon?</font>

172
00:13:05,700 --> 00:13:09,700
<font color=#DEDE00>Wah. Kalau kupikir-pikir, aku orang yang
