175
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:20,900
<font color=#DEDE00>Kau layak diperlakukan seperti ini.</font>

176
00:13:22,500 --> 00:13:24,300
<font color=#DEDE00>Makan seperti ini....</font>

177
00:13:25,600 --> 00:13:27,900
