188
00:13:56,800 --> 00:13:58,500
<font color=#DEDE00>- Makan semurmu.
- Pasti.</font>

189
00:14:00,400 --> 00:14:02,900
<font color=#DEDE00>Ya, Chan Gyu.
Apa kau membaca SMSku?</font>

190
00:14:02,900 --> 00:14:07,400
<font color=#DEDE00>Benar, Baek Shi Yoon.
Kau akan memantaunya mulai sekarang.</font>

191
00:14:07,400 --> 00:14:10,600
<font color=#DEDE00>Maka itu berarti Shi Yoon
