192
00:14:10,600 --> 00:14:11,700
<font color=#DEDE00><i>Benar.</i></font>

193
00:14:11,700 --> 00:14:15,800
<font color=#DEDE00>Kurasa aku melihat
tatapan membunuh di matanya.</font>

194
00:14:15,800 --> 00:14:18,500
<font color=#DEDE00>Kira-kira pekerjaan macam apa
