234
00:16:21,600 --> 00:16:24,100
<font color=#DEDE00>Oh, tentu.
Tentu kau harus khawatir.</font>

235
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:28,900
<font color=#DEDE00>Aku tak khawatir itu karena
