244
00:17:11,600 --> 00:17:13,900
<font color=#DEDE00>Aku mau minta tolong.</font>

245
00:17:13,900 --> 00:17:15,700
<font color=#DEDE00>Aku sangat lapar.</font>

246
00:17:15,700 --> 00:17:17,300
<font color=#DEDE00>Bisakah kau keluar
