272
00:18:47,400 --> 00:18:49,800
<font color=#DEDE00>Seperti itulah pekerjaan ini.</font>

273
00:18:50,400 --> 00:18:51,400
<font color=#DEDE00>Dan...</font>

274
00:18:52,900 --> 00:18:54,100
<font color=#DEDE00>Ini.</font>

275
00:18:54,100 --> 00:18:58,500
<font color=#DEDE00>Ini mungkin terlihat seperti bulpen,
