280
00:19:10,200 --> 00:19:12,100
<font color=#DEDE00>Tidak, mereka menjual ini di internet.</font>

281
00:19:13,100 --> 00:19:15,700
<font color=#DEDE00>Jadi, Chan Gyu ingin
