292
00:19:44,100 --> 00:19:46,400
<font color=#DEDE00>Anda tak bercanda, kan?</font>

293
00:19:48,000 --> 00:19:49,800
<font color=#DEDE00>Yang kumaksud adalah...</font>

294
00:19:49,800 --> 00:19:53,000
<font color=#DEDE00>Kau seseorang yang dibutuhkan...</font>

295
00:19:53,000 --> 00:19:54,800
<font color=#DEDE00>Kau seperti garam.</font>

296
00:19:54,800 --> 00:19:57,500
<font color=#DEDE00>Kau seperti permata yang bekerja
