662
00:47:26,700 --> 00:47:29,200
<font color=#DEDE00>Ya, tapi bagaimana kalian saling kenal? </font>

663
00:47:29,200 --> 00:47:34,600
<font color=#DEDE00>Kudengar untuk pertama kalinya kemarin 
kalau Mall Hallyu Core terguncang.</font>

664
00:47:34,600 --> 00:47:38,500
<font color=#DEDE00>- Kudengar ada si Bayangan.
